nodes.text: Cells 49557Ceta was a prison complex of the Galactic Republic. Located in the undercity of Coruscant, it was a high-security establishment made to hold humanoid prisoners awaiting shipment to permanent off-planet prisons. It was permeated by a sense of despair that was said to be its best defense.
Khaleen Hentz was imprisoned in Cells 49557Ceta for a time in 21 BBY.
